===Alternative forms===
The bottom component is written [[王]] in simplified Chinese and Japanese (as found in the {{w|Kangxi dictionary}}). However, in traditional Chinese the component is written [[𡈼]] instead, and in Korean it is written [[壬]] instead (the topmost horizontal stroke, [[丿]] slants from upper right towards lower left).

